---
/* Mentor Section — Lilian's bio */
---

<section class="bg-glacial-surface border-y border-glacial-bg py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Photo area -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-5/12 reveal-left">
        <div class="relative group">
          <!-- Decorative frame 1 (cyan) -->
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-cyan/20 group-hover:border-cyan/50 transition-all -rotate-3 pointer-events-none"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <!-- Decorative frame 2 (indigo) -->
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-indigo/20 group-hover:border-indigo/50 transition-all rotate-3 pointer-events-none"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>

          <!-- Photo container -->
          <div class="relative bg-white p-1 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <!-- Placeholder (replace with real image later) -->
            <div
              class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-glacial-surface to-glacial-bg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-glacial-gray font-display text-lg tracking-wider uppercase">Photo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating name badge -->
          <div class="absolute bottom-8 -right-8 bg-clinical-dark text-white p-6 border-r-4 border-indigo rotate-2 shadow-2xl">
            <span class="text-cyan font-label tracking-widest text-[10px] uppercase mb-1 block">
              Ton mentor
            </span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-black font-display">
              Lilian Sevoumian
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Bio content -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-7/12">

        <!-- Heading -->
        <h2
          class="font-display text-[length:var(--font-size-h1)] font-black italic tracking-tighter text-clinical-dark uppercase reveal"
        >
          LE MENTOR.
        </h2>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <p class="text-2xl text-on-surface-muted font-light leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-glacial-surface pl-8 mt-8 mb-12 reveal delay-1">
          Expert en automatisation et IA. Make Partner officiel&nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;premier Fran&ccedil;ais certifi&eacute; niveau&nbsp;5. Plus de 500 automatisations d&eacute;ploy&eacute;es pour des entreprises de toutes tailles.
        </p>

        <!-- Social links -->
        <div class="flex gap-10 mb-12 px-8 reveal delay-2">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lilian-sevoumian/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-indigo font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-4 transition-all"
          >
            <svg
              width="20"
              height="20"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" />
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
            <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@liliansevoumian"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-cyan font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-4 transition-all"
          >
            <svg
              width="20"
              height="20"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 00-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 00.502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 002.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 002.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z" />
            </svg>
            YouTube
            <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote -->
        <blockquote class="relative p-10 bg-glacial-panel border border-glacial-surface italic text-xl font-light -rotate-1 text-on-surface reveal delay-3">
          <!-- Left accent bar -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-indigo"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <p>
            Mon objectif&nbsp;: te donner en 3 mois les comp&eacute;tences qui m'ont pris 4 ans &agrave; construire. Pas de th&eacute;orie inutile, que du concret.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="flex gap-12 mt-12 reveal delay-4">
          <div>
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-clinical-dark block leading-none">
              500+
            </span>
            <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-muted mt-1 block">
              automatisations
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-clinical-dark block leading-none">
              2000h+
            </span>
            <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-muted mt-1 block">
              &eacute;conomis&eacute;es par mois
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-clinical-dark block leading-none">
              5 ans
            </span>
            <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-muted mt-1 block">
              d'expertise
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
